spanGrp.span: Well you can recognise our people by their face.
nu bizım halh mm biräz görüker üzündän dägiš
Unlike Russians and Georgians, you can recognize Urum people by their faces.
o uruslardan gürjülärdän šeidan bizım halh biräz üzündän görüker ki šei urumdurlar hä
Our people differ from others with their customs.
ee bizım halh ädätlärınän biräz özgä halhtan šei eder atličatsa eder nätävür dierlar hä
sora bizım halh mm ee išlian adamdırlar bizım halh
They work and help their wives.
kömäk ederlär ojahta išlerlär ğaria kömäk ederlär
semeini adamdırlar elä ojah adamidırlar ojah adami
They like working and building houses.
Our people worked here and built house.
čoğ burda bizım halh aa išlerdılär yaperdılär ävläri
Well, they differ from Georgians and Russians a bit.
nu elä ištem näblem ambelä biräz biräz ištem var orda ištem atličatsa ederlär uruslardanda gürjülärdändä millättändä
